## Testing

```bash
./Scripts/run_tcg_tests.sh   # headless Godot test run
```

Fixture pattern: `TcgTestHarness.load_fixture_dict()` sets phase/state/zones; include channeled `runes` when testing power costs without pre-filled pool.

## Bug backlog

File playtest bugs locally: `python3 Scripts/bugs/report_bug.py new` → `Docs/bugs/entries/BUG-NNN-*.md` + `logs/BUG-NNN-console.log`. Promote to GitHub: `promote_to_github.py BUG-NNN`. See `Docs/bugs/README.md`.
